paragraphs.title: Download csv
paragraphs.text:
%sh

mkdir /tmp/data/
wget https://www.data.gouv.fr/s/resources/fichier-consolide-des-bornes-de-recharge-pour-vehicules-electriques-irve/20151008-182813/IRVE-201510.csv -O //tmp/data/IRVE-201510.csv
head -n 5 /tmp/data/IRVE-201510.csv

sudo -u hdfs hadoop fs -chmod -R 777  /user/hive
hadoop fs -rm -R /user/hive/warehouse/bornes
hadoop fs -ls /user/hive
hadoop fs -mkdir  /tmp/data
#hadoop fs -mkdir /tmp/hive
#hadoop fs -copyFromLocal /tmp/data/IRVE-201510.csv /tmp/data/
sed '1701,1801d' /tmp/data/IRVE-201510.csv >> /tmp/data/IRVE-201510_fix.csv
grep "Freshmile" /tmp/data/IRVE-201510_fix.csv
hadoop fs -rm /tmp/data/IRVE-201510_fix.csv
hadoop fs -copyFromLocal -f /tmp/data/IRVE-201510_fix.csv /tmp/data/

paragraphs.title: Create table (Spark)
paragraphs.text:
%spark
import org.apache.spark.sql.SQLContext
import org.apache.spark.sql.types.DataTypes
import java.text.DecimalFormat 

import org.apache.spark.sql.types.{StructType, StructField, StringType, IntegerType,DoubleType, DataType, FloatType , DecimalType}
//sqlContext.setConf("hive.metastore.warehouse.dir", "/tmp/hive")

//sqlContext.sql("SET hive.metastore.warehouse.dir=hdfs://localhost:9000/tmp/hive/warehouse");
val customSchema = StructType(Array(
    StructField("ID_station", StringType, true),
    StructField("nom_station", StringType, true),
    StructField("adresse_station", StringType, true),
    StructField("latitude",StringType, true),
    StructField("longitude", StringType,true),
    StructField("nom_porteur", StringType, true),
    StructField("type_charge", StringType, true),
    StructField("nbre_pdc", StringType, true),
    StructField("type_connecteur", StringType, true),
    StructField("date_maj", StringType, true),
    StructField("observations", StringType, true),
    StructField("source", StringType, true)
    ))
val df = sqlContext.read.format("csv").
    option("header", "true").
    schema(customSchema).
    option("delimiter", ",").
    option("quote", "\"").
    //option("treatEmptyValuesAsNulls","true").
    option("mode", "PERMISSIVE").
    option("charset", "UTF-8").
    //option("inferSchema", "true").
    load("/tmp/data/IRVE-201510_fix.csv")



//sqlContext.sql("drop table bornes")
df.registerTempTable("bornes")
//df.write.saveAsTable("bornes")
//df.describe("longitude").show()
